This is the www.jabber.se web application, written in Erlang, Javascript, HTML and CSS.

To build:

 #1 Build dependencies:

> cd lib/couchbeam
> make
> cd ../simple_bridge
> make
> cd ../nprocreg
> make
> cd ../nitrogen_core
> make
> cd ../..

 #2 Build web application:

> make

 #3 Configure

> cp etc/default-start.conf.sh etc/start.conf.sh
> cp etc/default-cf.config etc/cf.config

 #4 To run:

> ./start.sh

